# Quick Revision Table

| Traversal | Rule            | Recursive SC | Iterative SC |
| --------- | --------------- | -----------: | -----------: |
| Preorder  | Root Left Right |         O(H) |         O(H) |
| Inorder   | Left Root Right |         O(H) |         O(H) |
| Postorder | Left Right Root |         O(H) |         O(N) |

### Time Complexity for all

```text
O(N)
```

because every node is visited once.

